{"name": "Orb of N4N9N1N;N5N:ON9N:N. 1", "description": "The Press is corrupt. An opaque shade obscures bias. I propose we remove this layer, which can threaten the function of our World Computer, and lay bare the origins of published information.

We aim to create b�THE JOURNAL PROTOCOL V1b� in the style of Nouns. Each day the protocol will auction an NFT and the winner may inscribe it. 97.5% of the auction proceeds will be directed to the treasury, 2.5% used for protocol maintenance.

This model creates a flywheel for the ongoing funding of software which serves the public good, as well as an open platform for publishing news, research, experimental data, opinion, art, and advertisement. 

It is useful to gather information into records so that the public may find it more easily.

Sales of Orb of N4N9N1N;N5N:ON9N:N. will fund smart contract and front end development. Leftover funds will be directed to Gitcoin. Orb of N4N9N1N;N5N:ON9N:N. will function as the primitive governance token. Open edition will close if funding is reached.

NON EXCIDET

-MM (Marin Mersenne)
